title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 1 2021

description:
Biden lies rain down in every direction. Nobody in the Biden administration is going to lose their job over the Afghanistan disaster. What will the left not lie about? Buck: "The primary counterterrorism mission under the Biden administration, is bizarrely and psychotically, Trump voters." California Recall: Front line in the Battle for Freedom. Call everyone you know about it, Clay recommends, it's that important for political accountability! CDC says unvaccinated should not travel over holiday weekend. President Trump to C&B: Rush would be proud.
